/* ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ helpers ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ */
const isoCountry = (label) => ({
  Ukraine: 'UA',
  Poland : 'PL',
  Germany: 'DE',
  'United States': 'US',
}[label] || label);                 // fallback: use the label itself

const firstPlain = (rt = []) => rt.map(r => r.plain_text).join('\n');

/* ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ gather inputs ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ */
const webhook = $('Create requisition button').first().json.body.data;
const props   = webhook.properties;

/* Notion look‚Äëups already performed upstream */
const deptNode  = $('Find Department page').first().json;
const roleNode  = $('Find Role page').first().json;
const teamNode  = $('Find Team page').first().json;
const userNode  = $('convert to json object4').first().json;

/* IDs & names */
const ttRich = ;
const ttId   = ttRich.length ? ttRich[0].plain_text.trim() : null;
const isUpdate = !!ttId;                           // ‚Üê create vs update

const departmentId = deptNode?.property_tt_department_id?.trim() || null;
const roleId       = roleNode?.property_tt_role_id?.trim()         || null;
const teamName     = teamNode?.name                                || null;
const userId       = userNode?.data?.[0]?.id?.trim()               || null;

/* ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ salary logic ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ */
const wantRange = props['Need salary range?']?.checkbox ?? true;
let minSalary   = null;
let maxSalary   = null;

if (wantRange) {
  minSalary = props['Min Salary']?.number ?? null;
  maxSalary = props['Max Salary']?.number ?? null;
} else {
  const fixed = props['Fixed Salary']?.number ?? null;
  if (fixed !== null) {
    minSalary = fixed - 1;      // TT requires both even if equal
    maxSalary = fixed;
  }
}

/* ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ relationships ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ */
const relationships = {
  location:  { data: { id: '1200146', type: 'locations'  } },  // constant
};
if (departmentId) relationships.department = { data: { id: departmentId, type: 'departments' } };
if (roleId)       relationships.role       = { data: { id: roleId,       type: 'roles'       } };
if (userId)       relationships.user       = { data: { id: userId,       type: 'users'       } };

/* ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ payload ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ */
const payload = {
  data: {
    type: 'requisitions',
    ...(isUpdate ? { id: ttId } : {}),            // add id only on update
    attributes: {
      'job-title':          props.Name?.title?.[0]?.plain_text ?? '',
      'job-description':    firstPlain(props['Job Description']?.rich_text),
      country:              isoCountry(props['Country*']?.select?.name ?? ''),
      'min-salary':         minSalary,
      'max-salary':         maxSalary,
      currency:             'USD',
      'salary-time-unit':   (props['Salary Period*']?.select?.name ?? '').toLowerCase(),
      'number-of-openings': props['Expected number of hires*']?.number ?? null,
      'custom-form-answers': {
        desire_start_day:       props['Desire start Day of newcomer*']?.date?.start ?? null,
        priority_of_position:   props['Priority of position']?.select?.name ?? null,
        level_of_candidate:     props['Level of Candidate*']?.select?.name ?? null,
        team:                   teamName,
        reason:                 (props['Reason*']?.multi_select ?? []).map(s => s.name).join(', '),
        will_there_be_a_test_task:
                                 props['Will there be a test task?']?.select?.name ?? null,
        please_define_hiring_stages:
                                 (props['Please define hiring stages']?.multi_select ?? [])
                                   .map(s => s.name).join(', '),
        key_competencies_for_position:
                                 firstPlain(props['Key Competencies for position']?.rich_text),
        additional_comments_for_recruiter_or_approval:
                                 firstPlain(props['Additional Comments for Recruiter or Approval']?.rich_text)
      },
      status: 'pending'
    },
    relationships
  }
};

/* ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ output ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ */
return {
  payload,
  isUpdate,
  ttId,
};

// Strip the ID so Teamtailor accepts a POST.
const p = $('Assemble Body Universal').first().json.payload;          // shallow copy

if (p?.data?.id) delete p.data.id;

return { payload: p };                   // nothing else needed

